Bilfinger Seeks New Name, India Acquisitions, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 
2011-11-29T06:43:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/bilfinger-seeks-new-name-india-acquisitions-handelsblatt-says.html
Bilfinger Berger SE , Germany’s
second-largest builder, may change its name by the beginning of
next year to reflect the company’s new focus on services,
 Handelsblatt  said, citing an interview with Chief Executive
Officer  Roland Koch .  Bilfinger’s acquisition of  India ’s Neo Structo Construction
Ltd. is the basis for further purchases in the country, Koch
told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
 snicola2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  